page_0: "There is a secret door at the end of the cell block which can be opened by a switch in the captain's room. The door leads to the Mechanists' 'Advanced Interrogation Facility', the place everybody calls 'The Meat Mincer'.
Apparantly it is the place they keep political prisoners and put them under the most horrible mental and physical torture imaginable, in the name of religion. Even thinking about it gives me the shivers.

And to think that stupid taffer Benny wants to sneak in there and see what it looks like inside!"